    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Small vessels, usually ancient, having the shape of a jug, which is a vessel with a narrow neck, handle, and pouring lip.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
